以下是一个基本的 Java 实现完整灯塔 AOI 算法的代码，仅供参考：

1. 定义灯塔坐标和灯塔类：

```java
public class Tower {
    private final double x;
    private final double y;
    private final double radius;
    private final List<Player> players = new ArrayList<>(); // 存储灯塔内的所有玩家

    public Tower(double x, double y, double radius) {
        this.x = x;
        this.y = y;
        this.radius = radius;
    }

    public double getX() {
        return x;
    }

    public double getY() {
        return y;
    }

    public double getRadius() {
        return radius;
    }

    public List<Player> getPlayers() {
        return players;
    }

    public void addPlayer(Player player) {
        players.add(player);
    }

    public boolean removePlayer(Player player) {
        return players.remove(player);
    }

    public boolean inRange(Player player) {
        double distance = Math.sqrt(
            Math.pow(player.getX() - x, 2) + Math.pow(player.getY() - y, 2)
        );
        return distance <= radius;
    }
}
```

2. 定义玩家和玩家管理类：

```java
public class Player {
    private final int id;
    private double x;
    private double y;
    private Tower currentTower; // 玩家当前所在的灯塔

    public Player(int id, double x, double y) {
        this.id = id;
        this.x = x;
        this.y = y;
    }

    public int getId() {
        return id;
    }

    public double getX() {
        return x;
    }

    public double getY() {
        return y;
    }

    public Tower getCurrentTower() {
        return currentTower;
    }

    // 更新玩家的坐标
    public void updatePosition(double x, double y) {
        this.x = x;
        this.y = y;
    }

    // 进入新的灯塔
    public void enterTower(Tower tower) {
        if (currentTower != null) {
            currentTower.removePlayer(this);
        }
        currentTower = tower;
        currentTower.addPlayer(this);
    }

    // 离开当前灯塔
    public void leaveTower() {
        if (currentTower != null) {
            currentTower.removePlayer(this);
            currentTower = null;
        }
    }

    // 检查玩家是否需要进入新的灯塔
    public void checkTower(List<Tower> towers) {
        for (Tower tower : towers) {
            if (tower.inRange(this)) {
                if (currentTower != tower) {
                    enterTower(tower);
                }
                return;
            }
        }
        // 如果无法进入任何一个灯塔，则离开当前灯塔
        leaveTower();
    }
}

public class PlayerManager {
    private final List<Player> players = new ArrayList<>();
    private final List<Tower> towers = new ArrayList<>();

    // 添加新玩家
    public void addPlayer(Player player) {
        players.add(player);
    }

    // 移除玩家
    public boolean removePlayer(Player player) {
        player.leaveTower();
        return players.remove(player);
    }

    // 添加新灯塔
    public void addTower(Tower tower) {
        towers.add(tower);
    }

    // 移除灯塔
    public boolean removeTower(Tower tower) {
        for (Player player : tower.getPlayers()) {
            player.leaveTower();
        }
        return towers.remove(tower);
    }

    // 更新所有玩家的位置并移动玩家到对应灯塔
    public void updatePlayers() {
        for (Player player : players) {
            player.checkTower(towers);
        }
    }
}
```

3. 在引擎主循环中定时更新玩家位置和灯塔：

```java
public class GameEngine {
    private final PlayerManager playerManager = new PlayerManager();
    private final Timer timer;

    public GameEngine() {
        // 创建定时器，每 50ms 更新一次玩家位置和灯塔
        timer = new Timer();
